OL,3,CInside Haiti's humanitarian emergency
OL,4,Cwhere gang violence rules the streets
OL,6,FWords by Jonathan Dumont
OL,8,FAs Head of Emergency Communications
OL,9,Ffor the United Nations World Food
OL,10,FProgramme (WFP), I frequently travel
OL,11,Fto conflict zones to gather
OL,12,Finformation and video on the
OL,13,Ffrontlines of hunger.
OL,15,FIn the past year, I've been to places
OL,16,Flike the eastern Democratic Republic
OL,17,Fof Congo, Sudan, Syria, Gaza, and
OL,18,FHaiti.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
