OL,3,CInside Haiti's humanitarian emergency
OL,4,Cwhere gang violence rules the streets
OL,6,FAfter a security briefing, my
OL,7,Fcolleagues and I loaded into armoured
OL,8,Fvehicles to visit a school where 3,000
OL,9,Fpeople who fled the violence were
OL,10,Fstaying.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FMany of the displaced are children who
OL,18,Fhaven't been to school for months
OL,19,Fbecause they are living in classrooms
OL,20,Finstead of learning in them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
