OL,3,CInside Haiti's humanitarian emergency
OL,4,Cwhere gang violence rules the streets
OL,6,FSuffering is not new to this family.
OL,7,FRose can only walk with the help of
OL,8,Fcrutches due to childhood polio, and
OL,9,Fher daughter, Medegine, was raped and
OL,10,Fbecame pregnant with Nalaika when she
OL,11,Fwas only 14.
OL,13,FLast February, she and her family were
OL,14,Fforced to flee their home in the
OL,15,FDelmas neighbourhood when armed gangs
OL,16,Fattacked, shooting and setting fire to
OL,17,Fhomes. She recounted her story as a
OL,18,Fcoloured band was being fitted around
OL,19,FNelaika's tiny arm by a nutritionist.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
