OL,6,FHe pulled the band, and red appeared
OL,7,Fin the window of the band, indicating
OL,8,Fthat she was severely malnourished.
OL,10,FRose turned to me and explained: "I
OL,11,Fcannot afford to feed her mother so
OL,12,Fthat she can breastfeed her properly.
OL,13,FSometimes they go to bed hungry
OL,14,Fbecause I don't have a job, and it's
OL,15,Fcausing malnutrition. "
