OL,6,FRose was given packets of nutritional
OL,7,Ffood to help treat Nelaikai. I
OL,8,Ffollowed her as she deftly used her
OL,9,Fcrutches to manoeuvre through the
OL,10,Fschool yard, crowded with people
OL,11,Fcrammed in whatever space they could
OL,12,Fwith their belongings.
OL,14,FShe hopped up a flight of stairs on
OL,15,Fher crutches and showed me the small
OL,16,Froom where she, Nelaikai and Medegine
OL,17,Flive with 10 other people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
