OL,6,FShe looked at her granddaughter in
OL,7,FMedegine's arms and said: "I wonder
OL,8,Fwhen we will be able to escape this
OL,9,Fplace... I am not used to living with
OL,10,Fso many people... they swear and fight
OL,11,Fall day long... It's terrifying.
OL,13,F"I call for peace, an end to injustice
OL,14,Fand violence so that we can all go
OL,15,Fback home and live in peace."
OL,17,FThe next day, we drove in armoured
OL,18,Fvehicles through the rubbish-choked
OL,19,Fstreets of Cite Soleil - an area of
OL,20,FPort-au-Prince near the country's
OL,21,Fquasi-abandoned main airport.
