OL,6,FThey allow us to reach the unreachable
OL,7,Fand feed the forgotten.
OL,9,FIn a densely forested semi-rural area
OL,10,Fof Cite Soleil controlled by someone
OL,11,Fnamed YeYe, we met a young man named
OL,12,FAugustine wearing a gold skull around
OL,13,Fhis neck.
OL,15,FHe was surrounded by a group of
OL,16,Ffrowning boys wearing flip flops, low-
OL,17,Fhanging pants, knockoff Christian Dior
OL,18,FT-shirts, and carrying machine guns.
