OL,6,FThen I met one of the participants of
OL,7,Fthe project: Felix, 87 years old,
OL,8,Fstrong as an ox and razor sharp.
OL,10,FI struggled to keep up with him as he
OL,11,Fbrushed past the gunmen and showed me
OL,12,Faround the neighbourhood of ramshackle
OL,13,Fhuts.
OL,15,FWe came to the water reservoir that
OL,16,Fsadly dripped water due to the silted-
OL,17,Fup canals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
