OL,3,CInside Haiti's humanitarian emergency
OL,4,Cwhere gang violence rules the streets
OL,6,FHe listened to the WFP team explaining
OL,7,Fhow they were going to build a new
OL,8,Fchannel to contain and direct water,
OL,9,Fensuring a reliable source for
OL,10,Firrigation.
OL,12,FHe looked at me and smiled proudly.
OL,13,F"If we can get water back here, we
OL,14,Fwon't need food from you. We'll be
OL,15,Fable to feed ourselves."
